---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---
<Layout title="About" description="Jordan Fowler — AI Automation Architect, co-founder of DataKit, 20+ years building data systems.">
  <section class="max-w-3xl mx-auto px-6 py-20">
    <div class="flex flex-col sm:flex-row items-start gap-8 mb-12">
      <img src="/portrait.png" alt="Jordan Fowler" class="w-32 h-32 rounded-full object-cover object-top flex-shrink-0" />
      <div>
        <h1 class="text-3xl md:text-4xl font-semibold text-dtkt-blue mb-2">Jordan Fowler</h1>
        <p class="text-dtkt-dark/60 text-base">AI Automation Architect · Co-founder, DataKit</p>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="prose prose-lg text-dtkt-dark space-y-6 leading-relaxed">
      <p>
        I'm Jordan Fowler — co-founder of DataKit and a software engineer with 20+ years
        building data systems and automation tools.
      </p>
      <p>
        In 2013 I built Instalead, a social selling automation platform that helped sales teams
        generate leads on LinkedIn and Twitter. In 2026 I'm doing the same thing, but with AI
        and a data activation platform I spent three years building from scratch.
      </p>
      <p>
        Before DataKit: Director of Data Engineering at Lumenad, CTO at CapLinked,
        VP of Engineering at Cyndx. I've shipped production systems at every scale,
        from seed-stage startups to Fortune 1000 clients.
      </p>
      <p>
        I work with a small number of clients at a time — sales teams, recruiters,
        real estate investors, and B2B founders who have better things to do than
        pull data manually.
      </p>
    </div>

    <div class="mt-12 flex flex-wrap gap-4">
      <a href="https://linkedin.com/in/jordanfowler" class="inline-flex items-center gap-2 border border-gray-200 rounded-[0.6rem] px-5 py-2.5 text-sm font-medium text-dtkt-dark hover:border-dtkt-blue hover:text-dtkt-blue transition-colors" target="_blank" rel="noopener">
        LinkedIn
      </a>
      <a href="https://github.com/jordanfowler" class="inline-flex items-center gap-2 border border-gray-200 rounded-[0.6rem] px-5 py-2.5 text-sm font-medium text-dtkt-dark hover:border-dtkt-blue hover:text-dtkt-blue transition-colors" target="_blank" rel="noopener">
        GitHub
      </a>
      <a href="https://withdatakit.com" class="inline-flex items-center gap-2 border border-gray-200 rounded-[0.6rem] px-5 py-2.5 text-sm font-medium text-dtkt-dark hover:border-dtkt-blue hover:text-dtkt-blue transition-colors" target="_blank" rel="noopener">
        DataKit
      </a>
    </div>
  </section>
</Layout>
